text: Nick Hind (born 19 August 1994) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for the St Kilda Football Club in the Australian Football League (AFL). He was selected at pick #54 in the 2018 national draft. He made his senior debut against Gold Coast in round 13 of the 2019 season. ==References== ==External links== * *Nick Hind from AFL Tables Category:St Kilda Football Club players Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia)
